PrecisOrder making it known that the Governor in Council declines to rescind or vary NATIONAL TRANSPORTATION AGENCY Decisions Nos. 569-R-1993 and 572-R-1993 and Orders Nos. 1993-R-266 and 1993-R-269 concerning the abandonment by Canadian Pacific Limited of rail operations on the segments of the Canadian Atlantic Railway from Sherbrooke, Quebec to the Canada-U.S. border, from the U.S.-Canada border to Saint John, N.B., from Grand Falls to Cyr Junction, N.B. and from Kentville to Coldbrook, N.S.
